---
title: Crispy Brussels Sprout & Bacon Flatbreads with Balsamic Glazed Onion & Rosemary
description: We’ve got your new favorite flatbread toppings coming in hot, so move over, sausage and peppers! You’ll slather golden flatbreads with tangy cream cheese, then layer on a tantalizing combination of Brussels sprouts sautéed in bacon fat and rosemary-infused caramelized onion with balsamic vinegar. Sprinkle the flatbreads with crisp, smoky bacon just before serving, and boom! Pizza night just got a mean green upgrade.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64f8885828f67f0f15b17e06-db7d0581.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64f8885828f67f0f15b17e06.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
